        <name>maxGroupSize</name>
        <qualifiedname>MR.MultiwayICPSamplingParameters.maxGroupSize</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>size of maximum icp group to work with; if the number of objects exceeds this value, icp is applied in cascade mode; maxGroupSize = 1 means that every object is moved independently on half distance to the previous position of all other objects; maxGroupSize = 0 means that a big system of equations for all objects is solved (force no cascading) </para>
        </detaileddescription>
